This file serves as an example.
Copy this to a new file named .env and fill in your actual credentials.

Flask secret key for session management and other security features
SECRET_KEY='a_very_strong_random_secret_key_for_flask'

Full database connection string for PostgreSQL
Format: postgresql://<user>:<password>@<host>:<port>/<dbname>
DATABASE_URL='postgresql://postgres:password@localhost:5432/kalaconnect'

Your API key for the Google Gemini service
GEMINI_API_KEY='your_google_ai_api_key_here'

Secret key for signing JSON Web Tokens (JWT)
JWT_SECRET_KEY='a_very_strong_random_secret_key_for_jwt'

The folder where uploaded product images will be stored
UPLOAD_FOLDER='app/static/uploads'